{
  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "**Audit Finding — P0 Critical**\n\n`vite.config.ts` is listed in `.gitignore` which means the build configuration is not tracked in the repository. This breaks the build system for every developer and CI.\n\n**Problem:** `packages/hx-library/vite.config.ts` is excluded from git. Without it, `npm run build` cannot produce the built output.\n\n**Fix:**\n1. Remove `vite.config.ts` from `.gitignore`\n2. Commit the config file to the repository\n3. Verify `npm run build` produces output in `dist/`\n4. Verify CI build pipeline passes\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] `vite.config.ts` is tracked in git\n- [ ] `npm run build` succeeds and produces `dist/` output\n- [ ] Package exports map points to built files, not TS source\n- [ ] CI build gate passes",
  "title": "FIX P0: Restore vite.config.ts from .gitignore (build system broken)",
  "status": "in_progress",
  "dependencies": [
    "feature-1772603426391-67xh8g56y"
  ],
  "complexity": "small",
  "priority": 1,
  "source": "api",
  "trustTier": 1,
  "quarantineStatus": "passed",
  "quarantineId": "bf4dd944-9f5e-4742-81eb-c56241ffccb2",
  "id": "feature-1772673556642-xzxp1mtds",
  "branchName": "feature/fix-p0-restore-viteconfigts-from",
  "descriptionHistory": [
    {
      "description": "**Audit Finding — P0 Critical**\n\n`vite.config.ts` is listed in `.gitignore` which means the build configuration is not tracked in the repository. This breaks the build system for every developer and CI.\n\n**Problem:** `packages/hx-library/vite.config.ts` is excluded from git. Without it, `npm run build` cannot produce the built output.\n\n**Fix:**\n1. Remove `vite.config.ts` from `.gitignore`\n2. Commit the config file to the repository\n3. Verify `npm run build` produces output in `dist/`\n4. Verify CI build pipeline passes\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] `vite.config.ts` is tracked in git\n- [ ] `npm run build` succeeds and produces `dist/` output\n- [ ] Package exports map points to built files, not TS source\n- [ ] CI build gate passes",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T01:19:16.642Z",
      "source": "initial"
    }
  ],
